    "title": "State Bank of India is Hiring: Credit Analyst (Senior)",
    "description": "Grow your career with State Bank of India! We are hiring a Credit Analyst for our Vijayawada team. Be part of a workplace that celebrates innovation, diversity, and performance.\n\nAbout State Bank of India:\nState Bank of India is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Prepare MIS reports for senior management review\n• Manage accounts payable and accounts receivable functions\n• Develop financial models and projections for business planning\n• Prepare and analyze financial statements, reports, and budgets\n• Manage credit risk assessment and loan appraisal processes\n• Prepare annual reports and investor presentations\n• Conduct due diligence for mergers, acquisitions, and investments\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Arch / M.Arch from recognized institution\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Tally\n• Proficiency in Risk Management\n• Proficiency in QuickBooks\n• Proficiency in Ind AS\n• Proficiency in GST\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in Income Tax\n• Proficiency in IFRS\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Referral bonus program\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Learning & development budget\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Vijayawada, Andhra Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with State Bank of India!",
